	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Scattering a bit of sugary food, you conjure swarming, biting locusts.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save constitution]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 4d10 piercing]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area is &amp;reference[lightly obscured] and is &amp;reference[difficult terrain]. Targets roll a save when they enter or when they end their turn in the area (but only once per turn).</p></li></ul><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d10 piercing]]{1d10} for each spell level above 5th.</p>",
